{"tid":2373919,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《最後生還者 2 》總監表示有意製作《制裁者》與《惡靈戰警》的電玩遊戲！？","createTime":"2021-01-20T23:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T11:40:50.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5be5d1f4affe0ae24312df6d2f77a2d257117f9a","tid":2373919,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:35:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59075&amp;fbclid=IwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D59075%26fbclid%3DIwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia7XxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=dc4c71ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59075&amp;fbclid=IwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8</a><br />\n<br />\n褒貶不一的頑皮狗工作室 2020 年度「鉅」作《最後生還者 2 ( The Last of Us Part II )》自發售前就話題不斷。諸如工作室副總，同時也是該遊戲製作總監 Neil Druckmann 的「不爽不要買」風波以及因為玩家反響過於劇烈而導致國外網站禁止「洗負評歪風」等不勝枚舉的事件，然而最近 Neil Druckmann 又大發豪語的表示工作室的下個遊戲目標將放在...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161114736737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161114736737.jpg&h=f104eef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是滴你沒看錯！據本人在推特接受 Greg Miller 提問時表示，他強烈希望能為漫威知名的反英雄《制裁者 The Punisher 》與《惡靈戰警 Ghost Rider 》「量身打造」電玩遊戲，詳見推特連結，而被點名的對象也包含了在美國大受好評的日本動畫《星際牛仔 Cowboy Bebop》！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161114827821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161114827821.jpg&h=ac40ee27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說回來，《制裁者》自從 2020 年 11 月起就沒有新的漫畫連載，最近又因為美國白宮的示威風波而受到影響，再加上 Neil Druckmann 的這番言論，真的只能用「雪上加霜」來形容...<br />\n<br />\n言歸正傳，自 2009 年 PS3 的《 The Punisher: No Mercy 》迄今，《制裁者》的電玩改編近乎「乏人問津」，或許 Neil Druckmann 這次的「發聲」，能讓更多人開始注意這個值得討論的反英雄也說不定？"},{"pid":"209cc0c3aaeebc3ad4e878264f6e7b97a8487141","tid":2373919,"uid":220431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:39:53.000Z","msg":"想像唔到punisher變大愛左膠"},{"pid":"6b28587d191f892c6fbe53cbb2505d7e45c25f9b","tid":2373919,"uid":43066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:58:09.000Z","msg":"屌 罰叔要變變性人同黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583e7969ef53c840dfb9192147cb8abdaf0c8f9b","tid":2373919,"uid":161935,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T00:14:34.000Z","msg":"ND整嘅就永久罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫大愛撚SJW去買，我道德無咁好，玩唔起神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a07f9bccca250eaab5ae94d39ed6962438e1b7c","tid":2373919,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T00:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573c8876b31e146f72a49177955bb52cae18fc15","tid":2373919,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"屌你開3個post"},{"pid":"27af132a90013f5ef9c4519709619b8263832c21","tid":2373919,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209cc0c3aaeebc3ad4e878264f6e7b97a8487141","tid":2373919,"uid":220431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:39:53.000Z","msg":"想像唔到punisher變大愛左膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T00:43:48.000Z","msg":"Punisher變boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb3272771149f6836dcf6e6b577f1f544572dcf","tid":2373919,"uid":40625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母垃圾驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acaac2db079ef7f032a3946ebce7f7ddf6